name: code
label: Code
description: A character or string that represents the short code name of the laboratory test. (NCIT:C83322 )

name: test
label: Test
description: A character or string that represents the full name of the laboratory assessment. (NCIT:C117142 )

name: description
label: Description
description: A written or verbal account, representation, statement, or explanation of something (NCIT:C25365 )

name: category
label: Category
description: A classification of the laboratory test. (NCIT:C83017 )

name: subcategory

name: genelist
label: Gene list
description: A data set of the names or identifiers of genes that are the outcome of an analysis or have been put together for the purpose of an analysis. (OBI:0000118 )
